1.4
log
@Move fontpath from /usr/local/lib/X11/fonts to /usr/local/share/fonts to match
XDG_DATA_DIR (where Desktop tools will look for by default).

discussed with sthen@@ and matthieu@@
ok sthen@@
@
text
@$OpenBSD: patch-modules_xttfm_ttfm,v 1.3 2013/03/11 20:59:05 sthen Exp $
--- modules/xttfm.ttfm.orig	Tue Nov  4 00:08:32 2003
+++ modules/xttfm.ttfm	Mon Mar 30 16:36:08 2015
@@@@ -28,7 +28,7 @@@@ export VERSION; VERSION=0.9.3
